@{fg shine} Zippy-Search @{fg text}is probably the most used searchtool for /X and S!X.
 However, most of the searchers previously released have not support for large
 dirlists, or more than 10 conference Dir(nr) files containing your File_id`s.

   I think of this door as one of the FASTEST ever for the /X or S!X, and it
    also includes many new features NEVER been used in earlier Z-versions.
               Just check out the screenshots before installing!


 A especially thanks to Kingpin/Spaceballs for the nice Beta-testing and good
           support + design ideas! - I hope you enjoy the result! :)


       The things that makes this Zippy differ from other searchers are:
    <Ŧ-------------------------------------------------------------------ŧ>

       Ŧŧ          Simple and easy interface toward the user          Ŧŧ
       Ŧŧ     Logical analyze of arguments provided to the door.      Ŧŧ
       Ŧŧ     Highly OPTIMIZED Assembler search-routines! (FAST!)     Ŧŧ
       Ŧŧ   The best Error-trap system ever made to a AmiX/S!X door   Ŧŧ
       Ŧŧ   Fully compatible with older versions of Zippy-Searchers   Ŧŧ


           - - - --- ------[ lizard of megastyle! ]------ --- - -  -

@endnode






